    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>Handle correct Return-Path header when sending emails via SMTP.</p>

<p>When sending email via smtp to the postfix mail server. postfix replace "Return-Path: " header to the ENVELOPE FROM header.</p>

<p>To prevent this behavior, and outputting correct Return-Path header i wrote a simple patch.</p>

<p>PATCH:</p>

